ge]] |location=New York |isbn=0-203-27706-6 |ref=M2 }}\n*{{cite book |last=Mills |first=AD |year=2003 |origyear=1991 |title=A Dictionary of British Place-Names |type=EPUB |publisher=Oxford University Press |location=Oxford |isbn=0-19-852758-6 |ref=M1 }}\n*{{cite book |last=Reaney |first=PH |editor-last=Wilson |editor-first=RM |year=1995 |title=A Dictionary of English Surnames |edition=3rd |publisher=Oxford University Press |location=Oxford |isbn=0-19-8631464 |ref=R1 }}\n{{refend}}\n\n{{given name|type=both}}\n\n[[Category:English-language surnames]]\n[[Category:Scottish surnames]]\n[[Category:Toponymic surnames]]\n[[Category:Surnames of Ulster-Scottish origin]]\n", "name_user": "Graham87", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eSurname:make proper HTML list forscreen readers", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crawford_(name)"}
{"title_page": "P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus", "text_new": "{{short description|Bus terminal in North Bengal, India}}\n{{Unreferenced|date=April 2020}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox station\n| name             = P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus\n| native_name      = \n| native_name_lang = \n| symbol_location  = bus\n| type             = Private Bus Terminus\n| image            = PC Mittal bus terminus.png\n| alt              = \n| caption          = Front View of P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus<br>P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus, Siliguri\n| other_name       = Dooars Bus Stand\n| address          = Sevoke road, Siliguri\u2013734001 Dist: Darjeeling, [[West Bengal]]\n| country          = India\n| coordinates      = {{Coord|26.7419495| 88.4346380|type:railwaystation_region:IN|display=inline,title}}\n| elevation        = {{convert|120|m|ft}}\n| owned            = PCM Group of Industries\n| operator         = Siliguri Municipal Corporation\n| platforms        = 28\n| bus_operators    = [[NBSTC]] and Private operators\n| bus_routes       = 10present\n| connections      = [[North Bengal]], [[Bhutan]]\n| structure        = Standard\n| parking          = Available\n| bicycle          = Available\n| disabled         = \u267f Ok\n| code             = \n| zone             = Siliguri\n| website          = \n| opened           = 03/02/2001\n| closed           = <!-- {{End date|YYYY|MM|DD|df=y}} -->\n| passengers       = 5,000 per day\n| pass_year        = \n| pass_rank        = \n| map_type         = India West Bengal#India\n| map_caption      = Location in [[West Bengal]]##Location in India\n}}\n\nThe '''P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus''' is a bus terminal located on Sevoke Road, [[Siliguri]], [[Darjeeling district|District Darjeeling]]. It is from {{cvt|5.4|km}} from [[Siliguri Junction railway station|Siliguri Junction]] railway station and  about {{cvt|8.2|km}} from [[New Jalpaiguri Junction railway station|New Jalpaiguri Railway Station]]. Both State owned [[North Bengal State Transport Corporation|North Bengal State Transport Corporation (NBSTC)]] buses and private buses ply from here. The Terminus is named after the famous P.C. Mittal, a social worker and a businessman, who was a resident of the [[Darjeeling District]]. \n\nThis bus terminus is maintained by Siliguri Municipal Corporation.\n\n== Amenities ==\n* Parking\n* Washroom\n* Restroom\n* Food stall\n* Bookstore\n* Newspaper seller\n* Information center\n* 24\u00d77 Transit\n* [[Ola Cabs]], [[Uber]], [[Rapido taxi]] service\n\n== Bus routes ==\n*Siliguri-Jaigaon\n*Siliguri-Malbazar\n*Siliguri-Coach Bihar\n*Siliguri-Alipurduar\n*Siliguri-Phuentsholing\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Bus stations in India]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Bus terminal in North Bengal, India}}\n{{Unreferenced|date=April 2020}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2018}}\n{{Infobox station\n| name             = P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus\n| native_name      = \n| native_name_lang = \n| symbol_location  = bus\n| type             = Private Bus Terminus\n| image            = PC Mittal bus terminus.png\n| alt              = \n| caption          = Front View of P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus<br>P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus, Siliguri\n| other_name       = Dooars Bus Stand\n| address          = Sevoke road, Siliguri\u2013734001 Dist: Darjeeling, [[West Bengal]]\n| country          = India\n| coordinates      = {{Coord|26.7419495| 88.4346380|type:railwaystation_region:IN|display=inline,title}}\n| elevation        = {{convert|120|m|ft}}\n| owned            = PCM Group of Industries\n| operator         = Siliguri Municipal Corporation\n| platforms        = 28\n| bus_operators    = [[NBSTC]] and Private operators\n| bus_routes       = 10present\n| connections      = [[North Bengal]], [[Bhutan]]\n| structure        = Standard\n| parking          = Available\n| bicycle          = Available\n| disabled         = \u267f Ok\n| code             = \n| zone             = Siliguri\n| website          = \n| opened           = 03/02/2001\n| closed           = <!-- {{End date|YYYY|MM|DD|df=y}} -->\n| passengers       = 5,000 per day\n| pass_year        = \n| pass_rank        = \n| map_type         = India West Bengal#India\n| map_caption      = Location in [[West Bengal]]##Location in India\n}}\n\nThe '''P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus''' is a bus terminal in [[Siliguri, North Bengal]], India. It is located on Sevoke Road, [[Siliguri]], [[Darjeeling district|District Darjeeling]]. It is from {{cvt|5.4|km}} from [[Siliguri Junction railway station|Siliguri Junction]] railway station and  about {{cvt|8.2|km}} from [[New Jalpaiguri Junction railway station|New Jalpaiguri Railway Station]]. Both State owned [[North Bengal State Transport Corporation|North Bengal State Transport Corporation (NBSTC)]] buses and private buses ply from here. The Terminus is named after the famous P.C. Mittal, a social worker and a businessman, who was a resident of the [[Darjeeling District]]. \n\nThis bus terminus is maintained by Siliguri Municipal Corporation.\n\n== Amenities ==\n\n*\ud83c\udd7f\ufe0f Parking Available\n*\ud83d\udebb Washroom Available\n*\ud83d\udecb\ufe0f Restroom Available\n*\ud83c\udf71 Foodstall Available\n*\ud83d\udcd6 Bookstore Available\n*\ud83d\uddde\ufe0f Newspaper seller Available\n*\u2139\ufe0f Information center Available\n*\ud83d\ude8c 24\u00d77 Transit Available\n*\ud83d\ude95 [[Ola Cabs]], [[Uber]], [[Rapido taxi]] service available\n\n== Bus routes ==\n\n*Siliguri-Jaigaon\n*Siliguri-Malbazar\n*Siliguri-Coach Bihar\n*Siliguri-Alipurduar\n*Siliguri-Phuentsholing\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Bus stations in India]]\n", "name_user": "Diannaa", "label": "safe", "comment": "Attribution: text in this article was adapted fromTenzing Norgay Bus Terminuson April 1, 2020. Please see the history of that page for full attribution.", "url_